I've come on a request from the guild. I'm Serena,
an adventurer.\n< Serena >
What's with this brat?\n< Man >

Has the fat finally reached your brain, you Geklan
fool?\n< Man >

I heard you were a trustworthy and skilled
adventurer.\n< Man >
Want to test me?\n< Serena >
Ah, that's right... huh!\n< Man >
What?\n< Man >

My Afa-Bile is impenetrable armor. Such a blow
won't cause me any pain or itch.\n< Serena >
Oh really?\n< Man >
And my left hand, the She-Cref,\n< Serena >
お酒消去
will crush bones and flesh with a single stroke.\n< Serena >
...Hmph. So you're not just some kid, huh.\n< Man >

That's my selling point. Those who meet me, like
you, first let their guard down.\n< Serena >

You've got guts. Alright, you're not bad as an
escort.\n< Man >
I'm Orca. Well, let's get along as best we can.\n< Orca >
Yes, that's my hope.\n< Serena >

*yawn*... I've been drinking too much lately...\n< Prostitute >

I love alcohol, and I can't get by without it.
Drinking makes me more popular too... But at this
rate, I'm definitely not going to have a good
end...\n< Prostitute >

If you don't know what to do, just drink some
alcohol and keep smiling; everything will work
out. Besides, they're paying, so you can drink for
free, which is awesome.\n< Prostitute >

Even if something unpleasant happens, getting
drunk can distract you, so you won't have to feel
too bad about it.\n< Prostitute >

But, if you get too drunk, it can interfere with
your work later on, and if you pass out, who knows
what could happen, so be careful.\n< Prostitute >

Some customers come here expecting that, and the
establishment won't help you unless it's to a
certain extent.\n< Prostitute >
...In the end, you've got to protect yourself.\n< Prostitute >

"Oh my, is this a new companion I see? How cute...
such a pity."\n< Prostitute >

For someone as cute as you, this job will be easy.
The men who come to places like this are blatant,
and if you let them do what they want, they'll pay
you a lot of money.\n< Prostitute >

But that means accepting to use yourself to please
the other person. If you choose that, you'll have
to endure and accept even the things you dislike.\n< Prostitute >

And remember, endurance is poison. A little might
be fine, but too much and you'll feel sick, and
won't be able to work at all.\n< Prostitute >

So if you really hate something, it's better to
have the courage to reject it. You might earn less
money, and the customer might dislike you and
leave, though.\n< Prostitute >

But in the end, that's how you can work for a
longer time. Not overdoing it and steadily
building up is perhaps the trick to this job, huh?\n< Prostitute >
